<p><b>JOIN THE IMMIGRATION CHAMPIONS</b>. In collaboration
with a neighbor church, we are organizing a team to
participate in the need for a strong public show of
support for a family in sanctuary sometime soon. This
will likely take the form of a vigil at the USCIS
building in Tukwila. We won’t know when—neither
date nor time—until shortly before the event and it
will be on a weekday. <i>Information</i>, 
<a href="mailto:cokello@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Join the Immigration Champions">Caroline Okello</a>,
